@startuml 业务架构图
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title TOGAF 业务架构图 - Single-SPA 微前端框架

' 业务目标层
package "业务目标层" {
  component [业务目标: 提供微前端框架解决方案] as Goal
  component [核心价值主张] as ValueProp
  component [战略方向] as Strategy
}

' 业务流程层
package "业务流程层" {
  component [应用注册流程] as RegisterProcess
  component [路由管理流程] as RouteProcess
  component [生命周期管理流程] as LifecycleProcess
  component [应用协调流程] as CoordinateProcess
}

' 业务能力层
package "业务能力层" {
  component [应用注册能力] as RegisterCapability
  component [路由导航能力] as NavigationCapability
  component [生命周期管理能力] as LifecycleCapability
  component [多框架支持能力] as MultiFrameworkCapability
  component [懒加载能力] as LazyLoadCapability
  component [应用隔离能力] as IsolationCapability
}

' 利益相关者层
package "利益相关者层" {
  actor "前端开发者" as Developer
  actor "企业架构师" as Architect
  actor "最终用户" as EndUser
  actor "开源社区" as Community
}

' 业务服务层
package "业务服务层" {
  component [应用注册服务] as RegisterService
  component [路由协调服务] as RoutingService
  component [状态管理服务] as StateService
  component [错误处理服务] as ErrorService
  component [开发工具服务] as DevToolsService
}

' 关系定义
Goal --> ValueProp : 实现
Goal --> Strategy : 指导

Strategy --> RegisterProcess : 支持
Strategy --> RouteProcess : 支持
Strategy --> LifecycleProcess : 支持
Strategy --> CoordinateProcess : 支持

RegisterProcess --> RegisterCapability : 需要
RouteProcess --> NavigationCapability : 需要
LifecycleProcess --> LifecycleCapability : 需要
CoordinateProcess --> MultiFrameworkCapability : 需要
CoordinateProcess --> LazyLoadCapability : 需要
CoordinateProcess --> IsolationCapability : 需要

RegisterCapability --> RegisterService : 通过
NavigationCapability --> RoutingService : 通过
LifecycleCapability --> StateService : 通过
MultiFrameworkCapability --> RegisterService : 通过
LazyLoadCapability --> RoutingService : 通过
IsolationCapability --> ErrorService : 通过

Developer --> RegisterService : 使用
Developer --> RoutingService : 使用
Developer --> DevToolsService : 使用
Architect --> StateService : 使用
Architect --> ErrorService : 使用
EndUser --> RoutingService : 受益
Community --> DevToolsService : 贡献

note right of Goal
  核心业务目标：
  - 构建前端微服务架构
  - 支持多框架共存
  - 提供统一的路由和生命周期管理
end note

note right of ValueProp
  核心价值：
  - 渐进式迁移
  - 独立部署
  - 技术栈自由
  - 团队自治
end note

@enduml
